This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) because it focuses on natural language processing techniques for information extraction. It could also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) because it deals with querying text. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.DB (Databases) because it discusses indexing schemes for efficient extractions. The paper also incorporates advances in AI techniques, which could place it under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
